item.title: March 2024
item.description: Mar 21 Mar 20 Last night, I cannot fallen asleep on time. Till a half past 3 A.M, I was awaking. There is a lot of thoughts in my mind. Especially some things like the passion or relationship. I think what I supposed to do is that make some changes. Mar 19 The more I worked for other people, the more I wanted to be my own boss. Duolingo’s sentences Did you hear that the teacher had to suspend Kevin from school for stealing?
